value.0: You better step back. Only those in the company of Mr. Hodge are allowed to enter his estate.
Well, actually, I don't much care one way or the other. If you are set on entering, I'm not going to get in your way. I'm not really much of a fighter and I wouldn't be able to stop you myself.
I'm supposed to be the butler, after all. I'm only filling in because the door guard died of plague. It would be your funeral if you dared enter, though.
Even if I wanted to, I'm not capable of actually stopping you. I don't make enough gold to get in your way. I say it ain't safe, but what you do is your business.
The guards inside are real tough. I'm sure they used to be ex-adventurers of some type. Like I said, it's your funeral.
